Drove to the mountains and walked around,

00:02:09.801 --> 00:02:12.781
like, a snowy little hiking path

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:15.760
because I didn't wanna see anything Christmas Eve I didn't wanna do.

00:02:15.761 --> 00:02:17.461
