00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:20.940
Like, do whatever the fuck it is that you wanna do.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.860
Sleep in bed all day, do whatever.

00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:24.740
And you know what?

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:27.840
I kind of found a little joy in, like,

00:02:27.841 --> 00:02:30.661
holy shit, this day is usually pretty fucking exhausting,

00:02:31.600 --> 00:02:32.700
and I actually,

